CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 13, 1959, pg. A16, reads: "Junior Aides - A new innovation for D.I.'s was the addition of junior aides as [to] their "Atlantic City U.S.A. review Sunday. Above are Paquita Sharp, Dole Ritter, Sylvia Davis, and Juanita Craxter."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of four D. I. Club Junior Aides, from left: Paquita Sharp, Dole Ritter, Sylvia Davis holding braided sun hat, and Juanita Craxter, posing in home of Gloria Golden Grate in preparation for D. I.'s "Atlantic City U.S.A." revue in the Press Club of the Hotel Sherwyn
